    <h1 class="fw-bold">Privacy Policy</h1>
    <p class="text-secondary">
        FinMate respects your privacy. Your financial records (income, expense, budgets, goals, reminders)
        are private and tied to your account only.
    </p>

    <h5 class="fw-bold mt-4">Data We Store</h5>
    <ul class="text-secondary">
